Package com.rb.biz.types.asset

Interface HasInvestable<T extends Investable>

All Known Subinterfaces:
HasInstrumentId
All Known Implementing Classes:
TestHasInstrumentId
public interface HasInvestable<T extends Investable>
Useful for data classes that pertain to a single Investable.

E.g. a buy amount can be for an AssetId (e.g. we bought this dollar amount of a stock) or for an AssetClass (e.g. we bought this dollar amount of an asset class).
